---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — KirbyDoesTech">
  <main class="relative z-10 px-6 py-20">
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-10">
      <header class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight">About Me</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          I’m Qurb E Muhammad Syed, a software engineering student who’s energized by building systems that are
          reliable, understandable, and built with care.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur-md">
          <h2 class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-300 font-medium">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M11.7 2.7a.75.75 0 01.6 0l8.25 3.5a.75.75 0 010 1.38l-8.25 3.5a.75.75 0 01-.6 0l-8.25-3.5a.75.75 0 010-1.38l8.25-3.5z"/>
              <path d="M3 10.94l8.1 3.44a2.25 2.25 0 001.8 0L21 10.94v4.56a.75.75 0 01-.45.69l-8.25 3.5a.75.75 0 01-.6 0l-8.25-3.5A.75.75 0 013 15.5v-4.56z"/>
            </svg>
            Current focus
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">Backend engineering, systems fundamentals, and cleaner architecture.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur-md">
          <h2 class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-300 font-medium">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3.75 4.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h5.25c1.03 0 1.9.69 2.18 1.63.28-.94 1.15-1.63 2.17-1.63H21a.75.75 0 010 1.5h-5.4a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v13.2a.75.75 0 01-1.5 0V4.5a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75H6A.75.75 0 005.25 4.5v13.2c0 .41.34.75.75.75h6.75a.75.75 0 010 1.5H6a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V4.5z"/>
              <path d="M17.25 5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0119.5 7.5v10.2a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H15a.75.75 0 010-1.5h2.25a.75.75 0 00.75-.75V7.5a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75H15a.75.75 0 010-1.5h2.25z"/>
            </svg>
            Studying
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">4th-year Software Engineering at Carleton University.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur-md">
          <h2 class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-300 font-medium">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M11.25 3a.75.75 0 00-1.5 0v1.037a8.25 8.25 0 00-4.965 2.87l-.733-.733a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.06l.733.734A8.212 8.212 0 003 12c0 1.49.396 2.886 1.087 4.09l-.733.733a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06l.733-.733a8.25 8.25 0 004.965 2.87V21a.75.75 0 001.5 0v-1.037a8.25 8.25 0 004.965-2.87l.733.733a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06l-.733-.733A8.212 8.212 0 0021 12a8.212 8.212 0 00-1.087-4.09l.733-.734a.75.75 0 10-1.06-1.06l-.733.733a8.25 8.25 0 00-4.965-2.87V3a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75h-1.5zM12 6a6 6 0 110 12 6 6 0 010-12z"/>
            </svg>
            Core stack
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">Java, C++, Python, SQL, Astro, and Tailwind CSS.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md p-8 md:p-10 space-y-10">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Who I am</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            I naturally gravitate toward back-end and systems work because I enjoy solving foundational problems: how
            data moves through a system, how code stays maintainable as it grows, and how software can be both
            performant and dependable.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            I care deeply about fundamentals and design clarity. I’m the kind of person who likes to understand why
            something works, not just make it work once.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What I’m passionate about</h2>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              <li>• Building complete projects end-to-end and polishing details.</li>
              <li>• Writing modular code that future-me and teammates can extend.</li>
              <li>• Learning system design, data modeling, and performance-minded habits.</li>
              <li>• Turning complexity into clean architecture and good developer UX.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Outside of engineering</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              I spend time refining my workflow, reflecting on how I learn, and finding better ways to create
              consistent progress. Discipline, curiosity, and long-term growth are values I try to bring into every
              project I work on.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="pill">Lifelong learning</span>
              <span class="pill">Deep work</span>
              <span class="pill">Design clarity</span>
              <span class="pill">Consistency</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/20 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Right now, I’m looking to build more real-world systems</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            If you’re a recruiter, teammate, or fellow builder, I’d love to connect and talk about software, projects,
            and opportunities where thoughtful engineering matters.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Find me online</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <a
            href="https://linkedin.com/qems"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-200 hover:text-white hover:border-white/30 transition"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-300" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M4.98 3.5C4.98 4.88 3.86 6 2.48 6S0 4.88 0 3.5 1.12 1 2.5 1 5 2.12 5 3.5zM.5 8h4V23h-4V8zM8 8h3.8v2h.1c.53-1 1.82-2 3.75-2C19.5 8 21 10.25 21 14.05V23h-4v-7.8c0-1.86-.03-4.25-2.59-4.25-2.6 0-3 2.03-3 4.12V23H7.5V8H8z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>linkedin.com/qems</span>
          </a>

          <a
            href="https://github.com/syedqem"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-200 hover:text-white hover:border-white/30 transition"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-300" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.58 2 12.24c0 4.53 2.87 8.37 6.84 9.73.5.1.68-.22.68-.49 0-.24-.01-1.05-.01-1.9-2.78.62-3.37-1.21-3.37-1.21-.45-1.18-1.11-1.49-1.11-1.49-.9-.63.07-.62.07-.62 1 .07 1.52 1.06 1.52 1.06.88 1.56 2.32 1.11 2.89.85.09-.66.35-1.11.63-1.36-2.22-.26-4.56-1.14-4.56-5.09 0-1.13.39-2.05 1.03-2.77-.1-.26-.45-1.31.1-2.73 0 0 .84-.28 2.75 1.06A9.3 9.3 0 0112 6.84c.85 0 1.71.12 2.51.36 1.9-1.34 2.74-1.06 2.74-1.06.55 1.42.2 2.47.1 2.73.64.72 1.03 1.64 1.03 2.77 0 3.96-2.35 4.83-4.59 5.08.36.32.69.94.69 1.9 0 1.38-.01 2.49-.01 2.83 0 .27.18.6.69.49A10.27 10.27 0 0022 12.24C22 6.58 17.52 2 12 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span>github.com/syedqem</span>
          </a>

          <a
            href="https://instagram.com/whoqurbae"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-200 hover:text-white hover:border-white/30 transition"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-300" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M7.75 2h8.5A5.75 5.75 0 0122 7.75v8.5A5.75 5.75 0 0116.25 22h-8.5A5.75 5.75 0 012 16.25v-8.5A5.75 5.75 0 017.75 2zm8.25 1.5h-8a4.5 4.5 0 00-4.5 4.5v8a4.5 4.5 0 004.5 4.5h8a4.5 4.5 0 004.5-4.5v-8a4.5 4.5 0 00-4.5-4.5z"/>
              <path d="M12 7a5 5 0 110 10 5 5 0 010-10zm0 1.5a3.5 3.5 0 100 7 3.5 3.5 0 000-7zm5.38-.38a1.13 1.13 0 11-2.26 0 1.13 1.13 0 012.26 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>whoqurbae</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
